---
title: Cheesy Pub Burgers with Griddled Onion, Chipotle Sauce, & Potato Rounds
description: We’ve officially broken pub burgers out of their dimly-lit all-wood setting and transported them right into your very own kitchen! Our ode to the gloriously-messy burger boasts all-beef patties, griddled onion rounds, sliced pickles, and a creamy chipotle sauce. Yep, the HelloFresh version is all that and a bag of chips—but better, because we’re serving it with garlicky roasted potato rounds. The only question left: what’s pouring?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-pub-burgers-76ad97f8.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/cheesy-pub-burgers-5dcb1c5982da1439e609cf39-186dd347.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/cheesy-pub-burgers-5dcb1c5982da1439e609cf39
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 980 kcal
  fat: 59 g
  saturated fat: 20 g
